ire row clickable\r\n\r\n* TransactionAdapter: Remove duplicate selectable_round_corner.xml\r\n\r\n* Payments/Sent Screen: Make selection darker and larger"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzcwNjc1MzA0", "url": "https://github.com/dashevo/dash-wallet/pull/342#pullrequestreview-370675304", "createdAt": "2020-03-06T22:55:23Z", "commit": {"oid": "245b2876940f34a886d2b035facd564767f77f9f"}, "state": "APPROVED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "035e7ad5916cd2b72660a49c0789267db70b28fb", "author": {"user": {"login": "tomasz-ludek", "name": null}}, "url": "https://github.com/dashevo/dash-wallet/commit/035e7ad5916cd2b72660a49c0789267db70b28fb", "committedDate": "2020-03-10T14:00:34Z", "message": "Fix crash when displaying tx details on Android 4.4 (#351)\n\n* Fixed the crash when displaying transaction details on KitKat.\r\n\r\n* Made the transaction details dialog background translucent also on KitKat."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "10f34a67a47de59c7e0d69a33fb8b2858aa3c07f", "author": {"user": {"login": "sambarboza", "name": "Sam B."}}, "url": "https://github.com/dashevo/dash-wallet/commit/10f34a67a47de59c7e0d69a33fb8b2858aa3c07f", "committedDate": "2020-03-10T22:19:25Z", "message": "Prevent sending while syncing (#339)\n\n* Use Repository to store/update BlockchainState\r\n\r\n* Prevent progress rewind\r\n\r\n* Save BlockchainState into Room.\r\n\r\n- Listening to Room changes to update state in several screens.\r\n\r\n* Prevent sending from \"Amount\" screen.\r\n\r\n* Handle blockchain reset and restore as the same"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "490922c8082076418639ca654085cdf0c6e49f55", "author": {"user": {"login": "HashEngineering", "name": "Hash Engineering Solutions"}}, "url": "https://github.com/dashevo/